###############################################################################
# Radish.Api - 聊天室 API 测试
###############################################################################
# 说明：
# 1. 聊天室接口均需登录 Token（Policy: Client）
# 2. 推荐通过 Gateway 测试：统一鉴权、路由与 CORS 行为
# 3. ChatHub 实时事件（MessageReceived / MessageRecalled / ChannelUnreadChanged /
#    ReadReceiptsChanged）
#    需配合前端或 SignalR 客户端联调，本文件仅覆盖 REST 主链路
###############################################################################

@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴通过 OIDC 获取的 access_token
@Gateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000
@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5100

# 测试变量（请按实际数据替换）
@ChannelId = 1
@BeforeMessageId = 0
@AfterMessageId = 0
@MessageId = 1
@SecondMessageId = 2
@ImageAttachmentId = 0
@TargetUserId = 1
@ClientRequestId = chat-http-20260718-001
@SearchCursor = 在这里粘贴上一页返回的 voNextCursor
@ReaderCursor = 在这里粘贴上一页返回的 voNextCursor

###############################################################################
# 频道接口
###############################################################################

### 1. 获取频道列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Channel/GetList?view=active
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. 获取已归档的一对一会话
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Channel/GetList?view=archived
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. 获取频道详情
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Channel/GetDetail/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. 获取频道在线成员
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Channel/GetOnlineMembers/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###############################################################################
# 一对一会话生命周期
###############################################################################

### 5. 幂等获取或创建一对一会话
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/DirectConversation/GetOrCreate
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": {{TargetUserId}}
}

### 6. 接受私聊请求
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/DirectConversation/Accept/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 7. 拒绝私聊请求
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/DirectConversation/Decline/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 8. 阻断会话
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/DirectConversation/Block/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 9. 解除当前用户发起的阻断
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/DirectConversation/Unblock/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 10. 归档会话
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/DirectConversation/SetArchived/{{ChannelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "archived": true
}

###############################################################################
# 消息接口
###############################################################################

### 11. 获取历史消息（最新 50 条）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/GetHistory?channelId={{ChannelId}}&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 12. 获取历史消息（向上分页）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/GetHistory?channelId={{ChannelId}}&beforeMessageId={{BeforeMessageId}}&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 13. 获取历史消息（向下分页）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/GetHistory?channelId={{ChannelId}}&afterMessageId={{AfterMessageId}}&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 14. 获取目标消息窗口（用于消息级定位）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/GetMessageWindow?channelId={{ChannelId}}&messageId={{MessageId}}&beforeCount=25&afterCount=25
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 15. 搜索当前会话历史消息
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/Search
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": 1,
  "channelId": {{ChannelId}},
  "keyword": "hello",
  "pageSize": 20
}

### 16. 搜索全部当前可见会话并继续 cursor 分页
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/Search
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": 2,
  "keyword": "hello",
  "cursor": "{{SearchCursor}}",
  "pageSize": 20
}

### 17. 发送文本消息
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/Send
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientRequestId": "{{ClientRequestId}}",
  "channelId": {{ChannelId}},
  "type": 1,
  "content": "hello from http test"
}

### 18. 发送图片消息（可选）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/Send
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientRequestId": "{{ClientRequestId}}-image",
  "channelId": {{ChannelId}},
  "type": 2,
  "content": "图片消息示例",
  "attachmentId": {{ImageAttachmentId}}
}

### 19. 撤回消息
DELETE {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelMessage/Recall/{{MessageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

###############################################################################
# 阅读回执接口
###############################################################################

### 20. 把个人已读游标推进到实际展示过的精确消息
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelReadState/Advance
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelId": {{ChannelId}},
  "readThroughMessageId": {{MessageId}}
}

### 21. 批量读取自己所发消息的回执摘要（去重后最多 20 条）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelReadReceipt/GetSummaries
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channelId": {{ChannelId}},
  "messageIds": [{{MessageId}}, {{SecondMessageId}}]
}

### 22. 普通 Private 消息读者详情（每页最多 50 人）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ChannelReadReceipt/GetReaders?channelId={{ChannelId}}&messageId={{MessageId}}&cursor={{ReaderCursor}}&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json
